  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Repurposed High-Energy Beam",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "改造高能光束",
    "TraditionalChinese": "改造版高能量光束"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "This Multi-Tool is made with material and methods known to no conventional manufacturer, its core a unfathomable array of impossible optics and glassy foam. Nonetheless, there is a layer of recogniseable technology. It shows signs of having been <span class=\"name name-stellar\">tampered with</span> by an unknown craftsman, who has repurposed its scanner array into a <span class=\"name name-technology\">high-powered mining laser</span>.<br><br>Powered by <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon-based Elements</span>. Fire the beam with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这把多用途工具使用了不同寻常的陌生材料与制作手段，装置的核心中安装了错综复杂的离奇光学工具与玻璃泡沫结构。尽管如此，其中依旧存在着能够识别的技术。有迹象表明有身份不明的工匠对其进行了<span class=\"name name-stellar\">改造</span>，并且将原本的扫描阵列转化为了一套<span class=\"name name-technology\">高功率开采激光</span>。<br><br>激光使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳基元素</span>作为能源。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>发射光束。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這個工具組由普通製造者不知曉的材料與方法製作而成，核心由大量難以理解的光學與玻璃泡沫組成。不過仍使用了一層可辨識科技。看似已經被未知的工匠<span class=\"name name-stellar\">修改過</span>，掃描陣列被改造為<span class=\"name name-technology\">強力採礦雷射</span>。<br><br>需要<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳基元素</span>驅動。使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 即可發射光束。"
  },
